comment.body:
Looking at some of the responses [here](https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/1573/workflows/d7ca1a83-a26f-455c-a249-58d5ec9f102f/jobs/14633) or [here](https://app.circleci.com/pipelines/github/open-quantum-safe/openssl/825/workflows/26d72f4f-7678-4195-bd14-fb3da4efe1d6/jobs/4154) for example, the usual returned state seems to be "pending" (the transition flow is described [here](https://discuss.circleci.com/t/pipeline-states/39687/2)).

I'm not completely certain, but my guess is that if the created pipeline does error out, that should cause a job failure and subsequent e-mail notification by CircleCI.
